How do you download individual comics now using the magnet torrent? Now when i click to download, nothing shows up in the box?

You just wait. When the file list shows up, you do it the crude way. Since I'm guessing you don't want to d/l all nine copies of Dobie Does Alice, you select all, right click ""don't download"", and then reset the priorities of what you DO want. This is assuming you have something like utorrent.
Time marches forward. Get another torrent client. There's no other answer, sorry."
